Document: EditorFileSystem
Path: godot/classes/class_editorfilesystem.rst
Summary: Provides access to the resource filesystem as perceived by the Godot editor.

Inherits: Node < Object

This class represents the resource filesystem as it is seen by the Godot editor. It allows for interaction with the project's files and directories, such as searching, importing, and managing resources.
